.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B LD_LIBRARY_PATH
Must include the directory containing
.I librtlsdr.so.0
(built by cargo in
.IR target/*/build/*/out/rtlsdr-build/src ).
The helper script
.B eti\-rtlsdr\-rust.sh
sets this automatically.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I dabctl.sh
Shell wrapper that sets LD_LIBRARY_PATH and runs the binary.
.TP
.I live\-capture.sh
Full live\-capture script (iq2eti | eti2pcm, saves WAV + metadata + slides).
.TP
.I test\-capture.sh
Automated functional test script.
.SH HARDWARE
Requires an RTL-SDR dongle (RTL2832U chipset with R820T/R820T2 tuner)
and a DAB antenna for Band III reception (174\-240 MHz).
.PP
The
.B dvb_usb_rtl28xxu
kernel module must be blacklisted:
.RS
.nf
echo "blacklist dvb_usb_rtl28xxu" | sudo tee /etc/modprobe.d/rtlsdr.conf
sudo rmmod dvb_usb_rtl28xxu
.fi
.RE
